OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShetland
OL,6,Fwill remain cloudy with the chance of
OL,7,Fsome mist and drizzle at times. Orkney
OL,8,Fwill be dry with variable cloud and a
OL,9,Ffew clear spells possible for a time.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FAnother mostly cloudy day.
OL,12,FShetland may see a little patchy rain
OL,13,Fat times, with generally brighter and
OL,14,Fwarmer conditions over Orkney before
OL,15,Fpatchy rain arrives in the evening.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FIt will
OL,18,Fbe a dry few days with plenty of
OL,19,Fsunshine, particularly for Shetland
OL,20,Fwith Orkney cloudier at times. Winds
OL,21,Fwill be light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
